title: T3 &ndash; June 2012 / UK (.PDF)
description: T3 : The Worlds Best Gadget magazine covers the world of gadgets and cutting-edge technology with photography and a blend of news, reviews, and features on lifestyle consumer products including cars, hi-fi, mobile phones, home entertainment, computing and gaming products, and more. T3 is the worlds no.1 gadget magazine, covering everything from MP3 players, to home cinema systems and games consoles. Its packed with the latest tech news, reviews and features and delivers a one-stop shop for the gadget-obsessed tech-oholic.
